<h1 class="rm-manual">BHA – Latest Information from Bali on novel coronavirus outbreak in China</h1>
<p class="rm-manual">By <a href="https://seminyaktimes.com/author/editor/" rel="author">editor</a> </p>
<p class="rm-manual"> Posted </p>
<p class="rm-manual"><a href="https://seminyaktimes.com/2020/01/">January 31, 2020</a> </p>
